TEXT.S: Baldwin Lonsdale( , Baldwin Jacobson Lonsdale) I a miheca saka folad saka a romi'ad masofoc ci Baldwin Lonsdale, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Vanuatu anini i ci Baldwin Lonsdale, patirengan a romi'ad i 2014 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 22 a romi'ad. kasofocan a loma' lalamod salikaka natayalan pitooran
